sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant Operator as TrustyAI Operator<br/>Service Account Token
    participant InfSvc as InferenceService<br/>serving.kserve.io
    participant Gateway as Guardrails Gateway<br/>8090/TCP HTTP
    participant Gorch as Guardrails Orchestrator<br/>8032/TCP HTTPS

    Note over User,Gorch: Flow 4: InferenceService Guardrails Injection

    User->>K8sAPI: Create/Update InferenceService<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    K8sAPI->>Operator: Watch Event<br/>InferenceService Watch
    Operator->>Operator: Check Guardrails Label
    Operator->>K8sAPI: Patch InferenceService<br/>Add Finalizer + Gateway Config
    K8sAPI-->>Operator: InferenceService Updated

    Note over InfSvc: InferenceService Deployed with Gateway

    InfSvc->>Gateway: Modified Requests<br/>8090/TCP HTTP
    Gateway->>Gorch: Apply Guardrails<br/>8032/TCP HTTPS
    Gorch-->>Gateway: Safe Response
    Gateway-->>InfSvc: Processed Response
